*sc3gzr*
Gamepad Controlled Real-time Text Stream Filtering with Audio Feedback

Perl/Supercollider
Requires Perl modules Linux::Joystick and Net::OpenSoundControl

More information can be found at http://t.dnlr.net/articles/sc3gzr.html

Photos from installation for The Ups & Downs (curated by Mathew Timmons) at Marmion Way, Los Angeles (November 13, 2008) can be found at http://www.flickr.com/photos/dan-richert/sets/72157623237796157/

